<paragraph id="82314AC94284A893F87C058B7BF99C1D" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Japan: Amami Oshima (
<bibRefCitation id="C71035D3ABABFAB36F730F93D4556469" author="Kifune, T" journalOrPublisher="Japanese journal of entomology" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="343 - 345" refId="B51" refString="Kifune, T, Yamane, S, 1992. A new Pseudoxenos (Strepsiptera, Stylopidae) parasitic on Stenodynerus rufomaculatus (Hymenoptera, Eumenidae) in Japan: Studies on the Japanese Strepsiptera XV. Japanese journal of entomology 60: 343 - 345" title="A new Pseudoxenos (Strepsiptera, Stylopidae) parasitic on Stenodynerus rufomaculatus (Hymenoptera, Eumenidae) in Japan: Studies on the Japanese Strepsiptera XV." volume="60" year="1992">Kifune and Yamane 1992</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
